IZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DGSwKcDUMAAbYDB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDGSwKcDUMAAbYDB.jpg&h=3b014f9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86b43bbe09bca7e6cff7849d5e1469233af148c9","tid":345633,"uid":59777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:00:42.000Z","msg":"井上拉麵個位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"567659e551506da03741d2d7918acb71422764ba","tid":345633,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:30:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鹽燒火炙拖羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e897ff05e3dfb43d06db583a30ee4a0fba9213c8","tid":345633,"uid":46644,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:37:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6262878ae67a85955ef0f0d7f30b36ad6dc7a109","tid":345633,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:44:12.000Z","msg":"深受國內外遊客歡迎的日本東京築地場外市場起火，當局出動30部消防車撲救，暫時未收到有人受傷或被困的報告。<br />\n<br />\n事發在當地時間周四下午5時前，築地場外市場一棟三層高的住宅起火，附近建築物受到波及。築地場外市場內有壽司店暫停營業，食客及店員匆忙逃生。<br />\n東京消防廳表示，目前共4棟建築物、約200平方米的範圍正在燃燒。大火目前仍未撲熄。<br />\n東京電力表示，因應消防部門要求，向火場附近一帶停止供電，目前共有約200戶停電。"},{"pid":"d8abf0f5264fcd8d97db87632c669faab338549b","tid":345633,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>燒得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55aa6ec4b55a74dadea95326bdb580dd61eb11ce","tid":345633,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017